config.value: SELECT      apt.AppTypeName    AS data1,      apt.AppSubTypeName AS data2,      sc.*  FROM      (          SELECT                            AppType                           data_apptype ,              AppSubType                        data_appsubtype ,              SUM(ul_flow)                      data3 ,             ROUND( SUM(ul_flow)/MAX(t2.ul_flow1) ,2.0)    data4 ,              SUM(xdr_count)                    data5 ,              ROUND(SUM(xdr_count)/MAX(t2.xdr_count1),2.0) data6 ,              SUM(delay)                        data7 ,              ROUND(SUM(delay)/MAX(t2.delay1),2.0)         data8          FROM              lte_sys.[@c0]_T_QUALITYSTATISTICS_ALLUSER t1 ,              (                  SELECT                      SUM(delay)     delay1,                      SUM(xdr_count) xdr_count1 ,                      SUM(ul_flow)   ul_flow1                  FROM                      lte_sys.[@c0]_T_QUALITYSTATISTICS_ALLUSER t3                  WHERE                      hour>='[@c1]'                  AND hour<='[@c2]'                  AND t3.[@c4]) t2          WHERE              t1.[@c4]          AND t1.hour>='[@c1]'          AND t1.hour<='[@c2]'          GROUP BY              t1.AppType,              t1.AppSubType) sc  INNER JOIN      lte_sys.[@c0]_T_BASE_CATEGORYTYPE apt  ON      sc.data_AppType= apt.AppType  AND sc.data_AppSubType= apt.AppSubType
